casebody.data:
Patrick Qulandis KENT
v.
STATE of North Carolina. No. 372P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 12, 2004. Patrick Qulandis Kent, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, C. Colon Willoughby, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 22nd day of July 2004 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the orders of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 12th day of August 2004."
